<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>First Stop: Reseller's Certificate of Registration</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#004080" LINK="#004080" VLINK="#0080C0" ALINK="#0080C0">

<img src="/dcca/graph/fs/fslogosm.gif" alt="First Stop Logo" width=171 height=120 align=left>
<h3 align=center>Department of Commerce & Community Affairs
<hr>
First Stop Business Information Center<br>
Business Requirement
</h3>
<hr>
<br clear=all>

<H3>I.	Business Requirement Profile: </H3>
<DL><DD>Reseller's Certificate of Registration</DD></DL>
<HR>
<H3>II.	Agency: </H3>
<DL><DD>Illinois Department of Revenue<BR>
101 West Jefferson St.<BR>
Springfield, IL 62794<BR>
Taxpayer Services Bureau<BR>
Central Registration Division<BR>
(217) 785-3707</DD></DL>
<HR>
<H3>III.	Statute:  </H3>
<DL><DD>35 Illinois Compiled Statutes 155</DD></DL>
<H3>Regulation:</H3>
<DL><DD>Title 86 Illinois Administrative Code Section 130.1401</DD></DL>
<HR>
<H3>IV.	Requirement Description:  </H3>
<DL><DD><P>Reseller's Certificate of Registration applies to businesses selling in a totally tax exempt manner, which are required to furnish a Certificate of Resale to their suppliers.  (An example of a Reseller is a manufacturer.) Registration as a Reseller allows a business to purchase and resell in a tax exempt manner.

<P>It is a Class A Misdemeanor to conduct such a business with out a certificate and may result in penalties including, but not limited to the following:  A tax lien against your property, garnishment of wages and bank accounts, recommendation of professional license revocation, civil judgment, revocation of business, certificates of registration, seizure and sale of assets, nonrenewal of corporate charter and/or criminal prosecution.  A Reseller's Certificate of Registration is valid for 3 years and may be renewed.</DD></DL>
<HR>
<H3>V.	Approval Process:  </H3>
<DL><DD>Applicants must complete an Illinois Business Taxpayer Registration application (NUC-1).  The average processing time for the application is 3 weeks.</DD></DL>
<HR>
<H3>VI.	Pre-Requisites, Co-Requisites & Post-Requisites:  </H3>
<DL><DD>A Federal Employer Identification Number (FEIN) may be required.</DD></DL>
<HR>
<H3>VII.	Fees:  </H3>
<DL><DD>There is no registration fee.</DD></DL>

<HR>
<STRONG>| <a href="/dcca/home.htm">DCCA Home Page</a> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/fsm1.htm">First Stop</a> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/fsbr.htm">Business Requirements</a> |</STRONG>

</BODY>
</HTML>
