<HEAD><TITLE>DCCA: News Release -- July 10, 1996</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000080" LINK="#000080" VLINK="#8080C0" ALINK="#004080">


<img src="/dcca/graph/logosm.jpg" alt="DCCA Logo" width=165 height=82 align=left>
