"Our task now is not to fix the blame for the past, but to fix the course for the future." President John F. Kennedy<p>

<hr>
<h3>BUMPER STICKER WISDOM</h3>

Talk Is Cheap.  Until You Hire an Attorney.<br>
Submitted by Tom Gainer, Springfield<p>

