The College of Life Sciences promotes academic excellence by emphasizing 
individual advising, high-quality instruction and academic challenges.  
Our Departments of <strong>Chemistry and Biochemistry, Entomology, Microbiology,
Plant Biology,</strong> and <strong>Zoology</strong>
