<center><h2>Call for Papers for Spring Meeting</h2>
</center>
<p>                               
Individuals who wish to share their innovative,
exciting laboratory exercises or other
instructional activities are encouraged to
contact <b>Ms. Susan McEvoy</b> @ 301-405 - 6897 (or
email at  <a href=mailto:sue@zool.umd.edu>sue@zool.umd.edu</a>) and request an
application form.  A presentation may be given as
a 30 minute lecture with audiovisual aids, as a
one hour model laboratory session, or as a poster
presentation.  Applications will be accepted
until 20 December 1996.
