A Final (but Important) Note from Your Fearless Leader</b><p>
<p>
	The entire staff is dedicated to making this course an enjoyable, worthwhile
learning experience.  We are very concerned about providing a comfortable
atmosphere conducive to learning.  We expect you work hard, but we also realize
that you will learn best by asking questions.  You, our audience and consumers,
should have input into the course and should demand our best efforts.  Don't be
intimidated or afraid; we are all on your side and stand ready to assist you.
Help us to help you by providing questions, criticisms, praise, etc.  Have fun
and get your money's worth.<p>
