        provide fast, informative and interactive content related
        to the College. You will find information regarding
        undergraduate and graduate level programs, continuing
        education, cooperating departments, class lectures and
        syllabi, online labs and institutes.</p>
        <p>The top level pages on this server are organized to
        give the quickest link to the variety of resources. You
        will find a consistancy among the pages and hopefully you
        will become comfortable in browsing through them. Much of
        the content on this server will be maintained by
        individuals (faculty, staff, students) with differing
        levels of HTML experience and as you delve deeper into
        the pages, the consistancy may change.</p>
