<p>
<a href="/zoology/welcome.html"><i>Zoology home page</i></a>
<p>
Recently ranked by the National Academy of Sciences as one of
the top ten zoology programs in the country among public institutions,
the department features distinguished faculty members whose research
interests are vast and varied.  The department also maintains a productive
and unique relationship with the National Institutes of Health, the National
Agricultural Research Center, and the Smithsonian Institution and National
Zoological Park through Adjunct research faculty
<P>
<i><blockquote>Admission to graduate study in the Department of Zoology
is restricted to students with adequate undergraduate preparation in the
biological sciences, as well as math, physics, and chemistry.  Admission
to the program is contingent upon the availability of a specific advisor
with compatible interests.</blockquote></i>
