	of the program will offer courses or are available to offer assistance in 
	conducting research related to the biology of small populations.  Many of these 
	are part of a group interested in <b><a href=http://www.inform.umd.edu:8080/EdRes/Colleges/LFSC/.FacultyStaff/dinouye/BEES/>
	 Behavior, Evolution, Ecology, and
	Systematics (BEES).</a></b> 
