<head>
<TITLE>Continuing Education - MCAT Preparation Course</TITLE>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<img align=left vspace=5 hspace=5 src="dnaspin.gif">
<center>
<img vspace=5 hspace=5 src=mcattitle.gif alt="MCAT Preparation Course">
</center>
<br clear=all>
An intensive 54 hour course of lectures given by experienced Life Sciences Faculty 
(Drs. Bellama, Khanna, Jackson, Mazzocchi, and Thompson).
<p>
Lecture and review of biology, organic chemistry, inorganic chemistry, physics, 
verbal reasoning and writing using the Cambridge MCAT program.  In-class problem 
solving, in-depth subject reviews.  Actual test simulations using full length official
 MCAT examinations.
<p>
In addition students will have access to Cliffs Studyware, and will receive a 
Betz MCAT guide containing in-depth reviews of each subject and review exercises.
<p>
Course Fee: $600.00<br>
<p>
<p>
