<H3>Jen's Oriental sauce</H3>
<B>Ingredients:</B><BR>

1/3 cup soy sauce<BR>
4 cloves fresh garlic<BR>
brown sugar to taste<BR>
touch of vinegar<BR>
touch of oyster sauce<BR>

<BR>
<BR><BR>

<B>Procedure:</B><BR>
Combine first four ingredients, stir, and wait for several minutes to allow garlic flovors to blend with soy sauce.  Add oyster sauce.  Makes a great marinade for beef with green peppers.

