<head>
   <title>Dr. Daniel C. Stein</title>
   <meta name="GENERATOR" content="Mozilla/2.01Gold (Win32)">
</head>
<body text="#000000" bgcolor="#FFFFFF" link="#0000FF" vlink="#551A8B" alink="#FF0000">


<img border=0 height=182 width=180 align=right src="stein.gif">
<h2>Dr. Daniel C. Stein</h2>
<p>Department of Microbiology 
<br>University of Maryland 
<br>College Park, MD 20742 
<br>Phone: 301-405-5448 
<br>Fax: 301-314-9489 
<br><a href="mailto:dstein@microb.umd.edu">email: dstein@microb.umd.edu</a>
<br clear=left>
<p>

<h2>
<hr>Academic Background </h2>

<p><b>Training</b> </p>

<p>B.S. 1977 University of Notre Dame, Indiana, Microbiology 
<br>M.S. 1981 University of Rochester, New York, Microbiology 
<br>Ph.D. 1981 University of Rochester, New York, Microbiology</p>

<p>
<br><b>Professional employment</b> </p>

<p>Instructor--University of Rochester--1982-1983 
<br>Assistant Professor--University of Maryland--1983-1989 
<br>Associate Professor--University of Maryland--1989-present 
<br>Affiliate Appointment--Assistant Professor, Center of Marine Biotechnology
-1986 to 1990. </p>

<p>
<hr></p>

<h2>Recent publications</h2>

