and modification systems of <i>Neisseria gonorrhoeae</i>. GENE 157:19-22.
</p>

<p>Drazek, E. S., D. C. Stein and C. D. Deal. 1995. Analysis of a gonococcal
gene encoding a homologue of the <i>Escherichia coli</i> ADP-L-Glycero-D-Mannoheptose
epimerase. J. Bacteriol. 177:2321-2327. </p>

