<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">

<HR>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER><B> ZOOLOGY 422</B></H1>

<HR>

<H2 ALIGN=CENTER><B> Mammalian Physiology</B></H2>

<P ALIGN=CENTER><B><I> Spring, 1997</I></B><BR>
 _________________________________________________________________</P>

<CENTER>
<P><B><FONT SIZE=4>Professor</FONT></B> : William J. Higgins : ZOP 2224 &amp , SYM 1212 : 405 - 2908 (for appointment) whiggins@deans.umd.edu</P>
</CENTER>

<HR>

<H4><B> Graduate Assistants:</B></H4>

<TABLE BORDER=1><CENTER>
    <TR>
        <TD ALIGN=LEFT> Mary Cho</TD>
        <TD ALIGN=LEFT> Ahmad Hariri</TD>
        <TD ALIGN=LEFT> Pam Lanford</TD>
    </TR>
