<H3><B> Recitation: (All recitation sessions held in Room 1121 of Plant Sciences)</B></H3>

<P> Attendance in recitation is mandatory; absences will be penalized by deducting all of the points from the recitation assignment that was conducted during the missed period. If you miss a session, you must attend another during that same week and check in with your T.A. and the T.A. in that substituted section. Arriving more than 10 minutes late counts as a missed recitation!</P>

