<BR>Some brief data summaries and reports are required. The data may be discussed with your peers, but all written work is to be the result of individual effort. Any deviation from this policy will be considered plagiarism. If you are in doubt about the acceptability of a group effort, ask your GTA! However, the <B><I> special project will be a group effort!</I></B></P>

