<H2><l1>Current Projects in the Paynter Lab							
</H2>
<P>

<P>
 <A HREF="project1.html"><IMG WIDTH=50 HEIGHT=50 ALIGN=RIGHT SRC="Images/MjtrayLG.jpg"><H3><li>
Evaluation of American Oyster Stocks for Resource Rehabilitation:  Disease Resistance and Genetics.</A></H3><P>
<BR>
<P>
