<UL>
  <LI> Filtration fraction = volume of filtrate formed per min = .25 renal plasma flow</P>
  <LI>Rate of urine formation = 10 mls/min<BR>
  <LI>B.P. = 00/50 mm Hg<BR>
  <LI>Hematocrit = 50%
</UL>

<HR WIDTH="70%">

<P> a) Clearance of Z<BR>
