encourage broad access to our services.  We believe that investors who
recognize the merits of investing in closed-end funds deserve to be
encouraged, and providing our services at nominal rates is our way of
helping you. We hope you will show your support by subscribing.  <P>
 
For additional information on rates and how to subscribe, please click <A
HREF="prices.htm">here</A>. <P>

